📊 5. Add Task Prioritization
Why this matters: Not all tasks are created equal, and the current output treats every structured task as the same urgency level. In real-world workflows, users need to immediately identify what requires action today vs. what can wait. Adding Gemini-powered priority detection turns a simple structured list into an intelligent triage system.
